{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"89ec877105","title":"对化工部关于第二个五年化肥预计发展报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"02ebe62c9d","index":0,"year":1958,"month":2,"day":3,"articleId":"89ec877105"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji38","name":"毛泽东全集第38卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/38-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji38":{"comments":[{"id":"13f7e4e9f2","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"89ec877105","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指化工部1958年2月1日提交的关于第二个五年化学肥料预计发展的报告。主要内容是：第二个五年计划到1962年化肥的预计产量；第一个五年计划化肥广建设项目建成后生产预计；第二个五年计划新建、扩建和原有的化肥厂生产预计。报告的说明中说：按照农业发展纲要四十条，我们曾将1962年化肥的生产水平定为700万吨，最近又重新研究了这个问题，认为根据各方面的条件，到1962年有可能进一步提高到1000万吨的水平。报告还预测了达到1000万吨化肥产量后将取得的经济效果和为完成这一计划所需要的投资、技术力量及原料资源等情况。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3670684f18","type":"title","text":"对花工部关于第二个五年化肥预计发展报告\"的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"89ec877105"},{"id":"13f7e4e9f2","type":"paragraph","text":"退总理：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"89ec877105"},{"id":"a7f31b464e","type":"paragraph","text":"可以印发。要署部长姓名。另注明“密件，注意保存”字样。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"89ec877105"},{"id":"fa93b148e6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"89ec877105"},{"id":"c62fce98ef","type":"paragraph","text":"二月三日上午三时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"89ec877105"},{"id":"2be36f2099","type":"paragraph","text":"重工业各部，每部都做出一个至儿个这样的文件，在几大内交来。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"89ec877105"}],"page":{"id":"6d616b305e","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"89ec877105","start":513,"end":513}}}},"__N_SSG":true}